OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FWindy, with some drier and
OL,6,Fbrighter intervals through the
OL,7,Fmorning, but also outbreaks of rain,
OL,8,Fmainly in the west. Rain becoming
OL,9,Fwidespread through this afternoon,
OL,10,Fwith a band of very heavy rain and
OL,11,Fstrong gusts clearing south. Further
OL,12,Fshowers following.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FWinds easing a little, but
OL,15,Fstaying brisk. Turning cold with clear
OL,16,Fspells and wintry showers, perhaps
OL,17,Fsome snow over hills. Some icy and
OL,18,Ffrost patches possible by dawn.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
